<h1>Orderly Book</h1>

<div class="docbody">
<p style="text-indent: 0;">Camp at Reas Town Thursday Octr 12th 1758</p>
<p style="text-indent: 0;">G. O.</p>
<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0;">Parole Bath</p>
<p>Colo. for to Morrow Colo. Montgomrie.</p>
<p>Field Officer to Morrow Majr Campbell.</p>
<p>Adjutant for to Morrow the Highlanders.</p>
<p>1 Capt. 2 Subs. 2 Serjts &amp; 50 Private to March tomorrow as an Escort to Waggons to Loyall Hannon this Detachmt is to give over the Waggons to the 3d Battalln of Pensyls. at Stony Creek &amp; then to return to Reas Town.<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0058-fn-0001" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0058-fn-0001-ptr">1</a></p>
<table class="bodytext" id="Col06d53t1">
